00:01:05.390 --> 00:01:07.820 align:middle line:84%
You're a slimmer Kenny today
and a married Kenny today.

00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:10.230 align:middle line:84%
>>JOHNSON: A married
Kenny and slimmer Kenny.

00:01:10.230 --> 00:01:11.730 align:middle line:10%
Married life does that to you.

00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:14.250 align:middle line:10%


00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:18.109 align:middle line:10%
When I met my wife, Pilar,
I was chubby, she said.

00:01:18.109 --> 00:01:19.900 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, but
you gave the best hugs.

00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:20.320 align:middle line:90%
>>JOHNSON: Yes.

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:21.160 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.618 align:middle line:10%
She still says,
when you hugged me,

00:01:22.618 --> 00:01:25.090 align:middle line:10%
you were like a bear hugging me.

00:01:25.090 --> 00:01:26.680 align:middle line:90%
She said, now, you're "flaco."

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:27.480 align:middle line:90%
You're real thin.

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:29.370 align:middle line:90%
I can hug you.

00:01:29.370 --> 00:01:31.440 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is true.

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:32.240 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:33.781 align:middle line:84%
So Kenny, before we
begin this, we're

00:01:33.781 --> 00:01:36.790 align:middle line:90%
doing a three-part story here.

00:01:36.790 --> 00:01:40.895 align:middle line:84%
And we have Doug Noll, who has
the project, Prison of Peace,

00:01:40.895 --> 00:01:43.600 align:middle line:84%
